<p>CLO collateral WAL test cushions play a vital role in allowing CLO managers to optimise underlying collateral spreads through trading, purchasing new long-dated assets, or amending and extending existing ones. This article provides an overview of EU CLO assets under management (in billions), broken down by reinvestment (RI) period and reported WAL test cushion, as of 31 March 2023.</p>
